Package: teads
Title: Datasets for teaching data science and data visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Gustavo",
           family = "Paterno",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paternogbc@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9719-3037"))
Description: An umbrella of worldwide social and environmental datasets for 
  teaching data science, R programming, basic statistics and data visualization in R. 
  The package contains a diverse selection of datasets to be used for teaching data analysis and
  statistics.
